WEBVTT

00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:03.003
♪MUSIC♪

00:00:04.371 --> 00:00:06.272
I AM AT THE LEFT
OF THE SCREEN.

00:00:06.406 --> 00:00:07.907
SO CAPTIONS
OF WHAT I SAY

00:00:08.041 --> 00:00:10.744
APPEAR AT THE LEFT
OF THE SCREEN, TOO.

00:00:13.313 --> 00:00:15.081
NOW I'M AT THE
RIGHT OF THE SCREEN,

00:00:15.215 --> 00:00:17.917
SO MY CAPTIONS
APPEAR AT THE RIGHT.

00:00:18.985 --> 00:00:19.953
<i> NOW I AM OFF SCREEN.</i>

00:00:20.086 --> 00:00:21.287
<i> TO INDICATE</i>
<i> THAT I'M OFF SCREEN,</i>

00:00:21.421 --> 00:00:23.723
<i> WHATEVER I SAY</i>
<i> IS ITALICIZED.</i>

00:00:24.591 --> 00:00:26.893
NOW MY NAME APPEARS AT
THE BOTTOM OF THE SCREEN,

00:00:27.027 --> 00:00:29.095
WE PUT CAPTIONS OF
WHAT I SAY AT THE TOP,

00:00:29.229 --> 00:00:32.031
SO THAT MY NAME IS
NOT COVERED BY CAPTIONS.

00:00:32.165 --> 00:00:33.033
UP UNTIL NOW,

00:00:33.166 --> 00:00:35.568
WE HAVE BEEN USING
POP-ON CAPTIONS.

00:00:35.702 --> 00:00:37.303
WHEN A NEW
CAPTION POPS ON,

00:00:37.437 --> 00:00:39.639
THE OLD CAPTION
DISAPPEARS.

00:00:39.773 --> 00:00:40.874
THIS IS A
PAINT-ON CAPTION.

00:00:43.009 --> 00:00:44.911
ONE CAPTION BLOCK IS
PAINTED ON THE SCREEN,

00:00:45.078 --> 00:00:48.648
FROM LEFT TO RIGHT,
ONE CHARACTER AT A TIME.

00:00:48.815 --> 00:00:50.583
NOW THE ROLL-UP MODE.

00:00:50.583 --> 00:00:51.651
THIS MODE IS NORMALLY

00:00:51.651 --> 00:00:54.120
USED FOR LIVE TV PROGRAMS.

00:00:54.120 --> 00:00:55.455
CAPTION LINES ROLL UP

00:00:55.455 --> 00:00:57.057
ONE LINE AT A TIME.

00:00:57.891 --> 00:00:59.492
Captions can appear
in lower case,

00:00:59.626 --> 00:01:01.361
and also in Spanish:

00:01:01.494 --> 00:01:04.564
¿Dónde está el niño?
Está en la casa.

00:01:04.697 --> 00:01:05.932
And in French:

00:01:06.066 --> 00:01:10.270
Parlez-vous Français?
Répétez, s'il vous plaît.

